{"id": "work_735ae479-713b-5a64-9d85-a4945e2ed887", "title": "Resolving photon number states in a superconducting circuit", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1023745423"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:37.244296", "abstract": "Count on qubitsIn cavity quantum electrodynamics (QED), atoms or quantum dots are made to strongly interact with single photons. Recent work showed that a regime of &#x27;strong coupling&#x27; can be obtained, where a single photon is absorbed and re-emitted many times. Schuster et al. have built a special type of cavity QED system that is embedded within an electronic circuit; in it a superconducting quantum bit (qubit) interacts with photons from a microwave transmission line. A novel regime can be produced in this system, namely the strong dispersive limit, where a single photon has a large effect on the qubit without being absorbed. This opens the possibility of nondestructive counting of photons that are present in the cavity. This effect could be used as a basis for qubit\u2013photon conditional logic, a requirement for quantum computing.", "publication_date": "2007-02-01", "doi": "10.1038/nature05461", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1023745423?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_78542dd0-c538-5434-8d2c-fe6f77c8cde3", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_14dc1e6b-eb21-5940-96fc-7d8b84783e30", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_1b8386ba-6df7-57eb-9e5d-a636a0c3dd54", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_db786820-6a2a-52d0-95c5-06b2dd7ce5d2", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_346a830e-67fe-5ca2-9afe-fc59ec3e813d", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_81b401fb-046a-541b-9444-170c08ed2c77", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_afd64421-6c30-5068-bae3-76e1ddd1daee", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_161bc9f4-7392-5c2b-9b2f-a41ce9b126d2", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_f3887ae3-1997-5c7c-bacd-477f516abf7d", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b7f874c0-f80b-59b0-ae92-d836f62f2b84", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_c0d42bc6-d071-559d-8c55-168d39330ed0", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_ad2f27f0-3b2b-5b24-ab7d-efc7258f0519", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_1237268d-b86c-5069-9aac-593eb92b7d86", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_33a238fc-438e-50ad-a807-7d90fcbbf23c", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_40c92d30-1e13-51c2-a6bc-692493c876ff", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_88296f4a-64f8-52e6-90c7-66edcf0854da", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_7ced97ac-1108-5195-b3a2-d664e9eb9af5", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_221a5cf0-5e73-5e2b-ba8e-2c0b66d37feb", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:36:37.244296"}